OL,3,CMan guilty of murdering and
OL,4,Cdismembering housemate
OL,6,FA horror film fanatic has been
OL,7,Fconvicted of brutally murdering his
OL,8,Fhousemate before sawing his body into
OL,9,Fat least 27 different pieces in an
OL,10,Fattempt to conceal what he had done.
OL,12,FMarcin Majerkiewicz, 42, even
OL,13,Fpretended to be victim Stuart Everett,
OL,14,F67, to throw friends and family off
OL,15,Fthe trail, using his phone and bank
OL,16,Fcards, as well as sending a birthday
OL,17,Fcard in his name to his brother, after
OL,18,Fhis death.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/13
