OL,3,CMan guilty of murdering and
OL,4,Cdismembering housemate
OL,6,FThe fate of the pensioner - who Polish
OL,7,Fnational Majerkiewicz had dismembered
OL,8,Fwith a hacksaw - was only revealed
OL,9,Fwhen a member of the public found his
OL,10,Flower torso and thighs, wrapped in
OL,11,Fcling film, in an abandoned bunker in
OL,12,FKersal Dale nature reserve, in
OL,13,FSalford, in April 2024.
OL,15,FFurther parts of Mr Everett were found
OL,16,Fin five other locations across Salford
OL,17,Fand north Manchester in the weeks
OL,18,Ffollowing, but only a third of his
OL,19,Fbody has ever been recovered.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/13
