OL,3,CMan guilty of murdering and
OL,4,Cdismembering housemate
OL,6,FCCTV revealed Majerkiewicz made
OL,7,Fseveral bus trips carrying body parts
OL,8,Fin plastic bags on "deposition
OL,9,Fjourneys" to get rid of the evidence.
OL,11,FPolice say they believe his love of
OL,12,Fhorror films and his "affinity for
OL,13,Fgore and torture" were "highly
OL,14,Frelevant" to how he killed and
OL,15,Fdisposed of Mr Everett in the
OL,16,F"particularly harrowing and gruesome
OL,17,Fhomicide".
