OL,3,CMan guilty of murdering and
OL,4,Cdismembering housemate
OL,6,FFollowing a three week trial, a jury
OL,7,Fof six men and six women convicted
OL,8,FMajerkiewicz guilty of murder, in
OL,9,Funder two hours of deliberations at
OL,10,FManchester Crown Court.
OL,12,FTrial judge Mr Justice Cavanagh told
OL,13,FMajerkiewicz, who made no reaction as
OL,14,Fthe jury found him guilty, he faces a
OL,15,Fmandatory life sentence but he must
OL,16,Fset the minimum time before parole.
OL,18,FThe court was told a murder
OL,19,Finvestigation was launched following
OL,20,Fthe gruesome discovery at Kersal Dale,
OL,21,Fon 4 April 2024.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/13
