OL,3,CMan guilty of murdering and
OL,4,Cdismembering housemate
OL,6,FDetectives found, two days before,
OL,7,Faround 5pm, a man was seen entering
OL,8,Fthe pathway nearby carrying a heavy
OL,9,Fblue bag, walking to the wooded area
OL,10,Fwhere the body part was found.
OL,12,FThe same person was seen to emerge a
OL,13,Fshort while later holding the bag
OL,14,Ffolded up.
OL,16,FPolice traced and arrested
OL,17,FMajerkiewicz, who was found to have
OL,18,Ftwo mobile phones, one belonging to Mr
OL,19,FEverett along with the dead man's bank
OL,20,Fcards, on him.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/13
