OL,3,CMan guilty of murdering and
OL,4,Cdismembering housemate
OL,6,FThey then discovered Mr Everett's DNA
OL,7,Fmatched the body part found.
OL,9,FMr Everett, originally from Derby and
OL,10,Fborn Roman Ziemacki to Polish parents,
OL,11,Flived together with Majerkiewicz and
OL,12,Fanother Polish man, in a terrace house
OL,13,Fin Winton, Salford.
OL,15,FMajerkiewicz is believed to have
OL,16,Fbludgeoned Mr Everett to death with a
OL,17,F"hammer-type weapon" at the home
OL,18,Fovernight between 27-28 March 2024,
OL,19,Fbefore dismembering him with a hacksaw.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/13
