OL,3,CMan guilty of murdering and
OL,4,Cdismembering housemate
OL,6,FWhen police searched the house they
OL,7,Ffound evidence of blood-staining and a
OL,8,Fclean-up operation, showing "something
OL,9,Fterrible had happened in that house",
OL,10,Fprosecutor Jason Pitter KC told the
OL,11,Fcourt.
OL,13,FA forensic examination found blood on
OL,14,Fthe carpet, wall and chest of drawers
OL,15,Fin Majerkiewicz's bedroom, with a
OL,16,Frectangular piece of carpet - later
OL,17,Ffound to have "widespread" blood
OL,18,Fstaining matching Mr Everett's DNA on
OL,19,Fit - cut out and replaced with another
OL,20,Fpiece.
