OL,3,CMan guilty of murdering and
OL,4,Cdismembering housemate
OL,6,FPolice used data from Majerkiewicz's
OL,7,Fphones, corroborated it with CCTV and
OL,8,Fbus journeys to spot a pattern,
OL,9,Fmapping his journeys, where they were
OL,10,Fable to find evidence at 15 locations
OL,11,Fand remains at four more -
OL,12,FChesterfield Close in Salford, Boggart
OL,13,FHole Cluff, Linneyshaw Colliery Wood
OL,14,Fand Blackleach Reservoir.
OL,16,FBut despite meticulous searches,
OL,17,Fpolice have only ever been able to
OL,18,Frecover around a third of Mr Everett's
OL,19,Fbody.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/13
