OL,4,Cdismembering housemate
OL,6,FPolice say they have never been able
OL,7,Fto establish a motive for the murder,
OL,8,Fbut believe the cause of the dispute
OL,9,Fmay have been financial.
OL,11,FSpeaking about the case, Detective
OL,12,FSuperintendent Lewis Hughes, said it
OL,13,Fwas "a rare and unique case" making it
OL,14,F"among the most complex category of
OL,15,Fhomicides that we get".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/13
