OL,3,CMan guilty of murdering and
OL,4,Cdismembering housemate
OL,6,F"It is a very unique case due to the
OL,7,Flengths the suspect has gone to to
OL,8,Fcommit the murder, to hide the
OL,9,Fevidence and make it very difficult
OL,10,Ffor Greater Manchester Police to
OL,11,Frespond to this and to solve it," he
OL,12,Fadded.
OL,14,F"There were 19 confirmed crime scenes
OL,15,Fand deposition sites in this case,
OL,16,Fwhich is a huge resource with
OL,17,Fimplications and investigative
OL,18,Fimplications for the force.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/13
