OL,3,CMan guilty of murdering and
OL,4,Cdismembering housemate
OL,6,F"But regardless of those challenges,
OL,7,FGreater Manchester Police have fully
OL,8,Fcommitted to solving this case,
OL,9,Fensuring justice, and returning the
OL,10,Fvictim to his loved ones."
OL,12,FMajerkiewicz will be sentenced on
OL,13,FFriday 28 March.
